Package services

package services
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AuthService
    The AuthService implements IAuthService, and is an abstract class that also provides functionality to verify password.
    AuthStaffService
    The AuthStaffService extends AuthService, and provides log in functionality for staff.
    AuthStudentService
    The AuthStudentService extends AuthService, and provides log in functionality for staff.
    CampStaffService
    The CampStaffService implements ICampStaffService, and provides camp related functionalities for staff.
    CampStudentService
    The CampStudentService implements ICampStudentService, and provides camp related functionalities for staff.
    EnquiryRequestService
    The EnquiryRequestService implements IRequestService, and provides request related functionalities for enquires.
    FileService
    The FileServices class provides methods for reading user data from CSV files and generating CSV files from Camp objects.
    SuggestionRequestService
    The SuggestionRequestService implements IRequestService, and provides request related functionalities for suggestions.
